sequenceDiagram
    participant CFG as Configurator
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant CM as Config Manager
    participant PF as Profiling Service
    participant SAN as Sandbox Env
    participant ADM as Admin
    participant MD as Metadata Registry
    participant NT as Notification Service

    CFG->>API: Upload draft configuration
    API->>CM: Store draft + validate schema
    CM->>SAN: Run sandbox validation tests
    SAN-->>CM: Return test results
    CM->>PF: Generate profiling baseline snapshot
    PF-->>CM: Return profiling adjustments
    CM->>MD: Record draft metadata + profiling baseline
    CFG->>API: Submit for approval
    API->>ADM: Notify pending approval
    ADM->>CM: Review and approve
    CM->>MD: Log approval, version info, and profiling baseline reference
    CM->>API: Promote to production tenants
    API->>NT: Notify stakeholders of activation
